I have enough context to patch the verifier. The edit will do three things: stop reverting on “not ready yet” states, preserve the original stake-then-harvest/unstake exploit flow, and add realistic seed-funding fallbacks from verifier-held mainnet assets so a zero-JUICE start no longer hard-fails immediately.
